<h2 id="flexispy">FlexiSPY</h2>
<p>Flexispy is an application that can be considered as a trojan, based on Symbian. The program sends all information received and sent from the smartphone to a Flexispy server. It was originally created to protect children and spy on adulterous spouses.</p>
