<h2 id="merlinx-equus-technologies">Merlinx / Equus Technologies</h2>
<p>Merlinx / Equus Technologies, Israeli firm, a privately held company specializing in the development of tailor made innovative solutions for law enforcement, intelligence agencies, and national security organizations. Linked to the Android malware, also sells iOS capabilities.</p>
