<h2 id="neosoft">NeoSoft</h2>
<p>NeoSoft AG, Switzerland manufacturer of Passive, Active (Semi-Active), Hybrid GSM Monitoring systems with A5.2/A5.1 deciphering, CDMA Passive Monitoring systems, IMSI/IMEI Catchers 2G/3G, InPoint SMS System (sends SMS to everybody). All NeoSoft systems support the following bands: GSM, PCS, EGSM, 2100, 850. NeoSoft has world-wide experience.</p>
