<h2 id="toka">Toka</h2>
<p>Toka, Israeli based company, which offers its police, government and intelligence clients the ability to obtain targeted intelligence and conduct forensic investigations as well as covert operations. In addition, Toka offers governments its Cyber Designers service, which provides agencies with the full-spectrum strategies, customized projects, and technologies needed to ensure the security and sustainability of critical infrastructure, the digital landscape, and government institutions.</p>
