<h2 id="darkmatter">DarkMatter</h2>
<p>DarkMatter founded in the United Arab Emirates (UAE) was under investigation by the FBI for crimes including digital espionage services, involvement in the Jamal Khashoggi assassination, and incarceration of foreign dissidents.</p>
