<h2 id="wolf-intelligence">Wolf Intelligence</h2>
<p>Wolf Intelligence a Germany-based spyware company that made headlines for sending a bodyguard to Mauritania and prompting an international incident after the local government detained the bodyguard as collateral for a deal went wrong, left a trove of its own data exposed online.</p>
