<h2 id="raxir">Raxir</h2>
<p>Raxir, Italy based surveillance firm that is housed in Naples, in a tech startup incubator. According to the company's page on the incubator's website, Raxir was founded in 2013 and produces software systems to support legal and intelligence investigations.</p>
