<h2 id="paragon-solutions">Paragon Solutions</h2>
<p>Paragon Solutions Ltd. was established in Israel in 2019. The founders of Paragon include Ehud Barak, the former Israeli Prime Minister, and Ehud Schneorson, the former commander of Israel’s Unit 8200. Paragon sells a spyware product called Graphite, which reportedly provides “access to the instant messaging applications on a device, rather than taking complete control of everything on a phone,” like NSO Group’s Pegasus spyware.</p>
