<h2 id="aegis">Aegis</h2>
<p>Aegis is one of the products offered by Semptian, a Chinese company, designed to be installed inside phone and internet networks. It is used to secretly collect people’s email records, phone calls, messages, geolocation data, and web browsing histories.</p>
