<h2 id="asia-global-technologies-agt">Asia Global Technologies (AGT)</h2>
<p>Led by Israeli entrepreneur Mati Kochavi, Asia Global Technologies (AGT) won a contract from the Abu Dhabi government in 2008 to create a “smart city” network of surveillance cameras, electronic fences and sensors that paid about $6 billion over seven years.</p>
