<h2 id="assac-networks">Assac Networks</h2>
<p>Assac Networks is an Israeli company that provides smartphone monitoring technologies. Its clients include other companies engaged in surveillance activities, such as Elbit Systems, Verint, and Rafael Advanced Defense Systems Ltd. Their mobile surveillance technologies are used by law enforcement agencies in Mexico, Colombia, Canada, Spain, and Singapore, amongst other countries. The company was also awarded a government contract from one of the Gulf Cooperation Council countries, although it is not known which one, as well as in at least 3 countries in Africa. In 2022, the company announced a major strategic investment and acquisition by ASPIS Technologies, Inc.</p>
