<h2 id="ateros">Ateros</h2>
<p>Ateros develops advanced wireless surveillance sensors to monitor Cellular, Wi-Fi, and Bluetooth communications, creating detailed communication fingerprints of targets. It claims to service customers in the Americas, EMEA and APAC regions. The products are primarily utilized for surveillance purposes by law enforcement, intelligence units, and at checkpoints and borders.</p>
