<h2 id="auterion">Auterion</h2>
<p>Auterion provides software platforms like AuterionOS and Mission Control to manage drone-based surveillance operations. These tools enable autonomous mission planning, real-time data management, and live video streaming. The systems support various surveillance tasks by integrating payloads such as NextVision cameras, designed primarily for defense, law enforcement, and use by government agencies.</p>
