<h2 id="authenmetric">AuthenMetric</h2>
<p>AuthenMetric is a Beijing-based facial recognition company and a contributor to China's AI-driven surveillance initiatives. Their capabilities include mass video surveillance projects with facial recognition, voice-recognition software, and comprehensive DNA collection programs. AuthenMetric's technology has been deployed at China's borders.</p>
