<h2 id="axis-communications">Axis Communications</h2>
<p>Axis Communications, a Swedish company known for its network cameras and other surveillance solutions, has a presence in the United Arab Emirates and sells its products there. In 2014, Axis praised mandatory video surveillance in Dubai. In 2015, the company was acquired by Canon Inc. The company provided its technology to China's public security system and was frequently mentioned as a "recommended brand" in Chinese state surveillance procurement documents from 2012 to 2019.</p>
