<h2 id="axon">Axon</h2>
<p>Axon is a company that provides surveillance technologies primarily for law enforcement agencies worldwide. Their Axon Network connects people, devices, and apps to create an integrated ecosystem that includes TASER smart devices, police body cameras, and digital evidence management systems. Their surveillance technology portfolio includes realtime crime centers through their Axon Fusus platform. Axon's AI-powered ALPR cameras include the Axon Outpost, which integrates livestreaming, ALPR, and vehicle recognition capabilities into a single comprehensive device.</p>
