<h2 id="bgh-tech-partner">BGH Tech Partner</h2>
<p>Boris Garfunkel e Hijos (BGH) is an Argentinian company that distributes surveillance technologies to law enforcement agencies. According to press reports, this includes facial recognition software as well as license plate readers. The company also sells Hikvision products.</p>
