<h2 id="blackbag-technologies">BlackBag Technologies</h2>
<p>BlackBag Technologies develops digital forensic and incident response software for analyzing traditional device data for Windows, Mac, iPhone and Android devices. It was acquired by Cellebrite, the Israeli company which works with police departments and government agencies to unlock phones for data-scraping purposes. It's funded by In-Q-Tel, which is a CIA-owned investment firm that supports U.S intelligence capabilities.</p>
