<h2 id="bold-technologies">Bold Technologies</h2>
<p>Bold Technologies, an Emirati company, is a supplier of cyber intelligence, forensics, and related tools to various government agencies. It's currently a partner in Abu Dhabi's $2.5 billion Aion Sentia initiative, an AI-powered smart city project launched in March 2025. It is working alongside Italian firm Negg, which is a developer of spyware technologies. The company is also partnered with China's Huawei.</p>
