<h2 id="briefcam">BriefCam</h2>
<p>BriefCam is a leading provider of Video Content Analytics (VCA) solutions, using artificial intelligence and machine learning to extract detailed insights from video surveillance footage. Their technology enables customers to rapidly review, search, and analyze hours of video in minutes, identifying objects, events, and patterns with high precision. BriefCam’s capabilities include real-time alerting, multi-camera search, and video summarization. BriefCam’s technology is primarily used by law enforcement and government agencies, as well as for "smart city" initiatives. In 2018, Canon completed its acquisition of BriefCam. The company’s partners include other surveillance entities such as Cognyte, Axis Communications, Pelco and IndigoVision.</p>
