<h2 id="calypsoai">CalypsoAI</h2>
<p>CalypsoAI, founded by Neil Serebryany, Davey Gibian, and Victor Ardulov, is a developer of AI surveillance and security technology, including the VESPR platform, designed for national security applications. Backed by investors like Hakluyt Capital, CalypsoAI has established itself as an intelligence partner for U.S. government agencies, including the Department of Defense, the Department of Homeland Security, and the U.S. Air Force. In late 2023, the company joined Palantir's FedStart program, which supports the deployment of advanced AI technologies for U.S. government operations.</p>
