<h2 id="camero">Camero</h2>
<p>Camero is a provider of Sense-Through-The-Wall (STTW) solutions, specializing in the Xaver series of tactical through-wall radar systems designed for military and law enforcement use. These radar-based systems enable continuous monitoring of individuals within a room while operators remain outside. The company was acquired by South Korea based SK Group, a leader in military technology in 2011.</p>
