<h2 id="cellxion">CellXion</h2>
<p>CellXion is a UK company that specializes in communications interception technologies. It has sold £1 Million worth of cellphone-spying devices to UK police. The company is one of the leading providers for IMSI catchers (covert communications data capture equipment that can track a phone's location and intercept phone calls and messages.)</p>
<p>According to Balkan Insight, CellXion received licenses to supply Serbia with wireless communication interception tools.</p>
