<h2 id="circles">Circles</h2>
<p>An NSO linked company providing technology that exploits SS7 vulnerabilities to track phones. According to leaked documents, Circles customers can purchase a system that they connect to their local telecommunications companies’ infrastructure, or can use a separate system called the “Circles Cloud,” which interconnects with telecommunications companies around the world. Circles Technologies was founded by Tal Dilian, a former commander of the IDF's Intelligence Corps Technological Units.</p>
