<h2 id="coolapp">CoolApp</h2>
<p>CoolApp is a locally developed messaging platform in Cambodia. Designed as an alternative to international apps like WhatsApp and Telegram, CoolApp aims to increase national control over digital communication and "reduce foreign interference". The app is endorsed by Cambodian leadership, including by the former Prime Minister Hun Sen, and experts claim it monitors users' activities on the platform.</p>
