<h2 id="cortica">Cortica</h2>
<p>Israeli company Cortica, and its subsidiary Corsight AI, has been using facial recognition and Google Photos to conduct mass surveillance of Palestinians without their knowledge or consent. Canadian-Israeli VC firm, AWZ ventures, is among its lead investors. Their tools are also deployed by the U.S. Department of Homeland Security for facial recognition purposes.</p>
