<h2 id="cyberbit">Cyberbit</h2>
<p>Cyberbit is an Israeli cybersecurity company that was established as a subsidiary of Elbit Systems, a major Israeli defense company, and which offers a comprehensive solution for monitoring and extracting information from remote PCs. The Ethiopian government targeted Oromo dissidents with Cyberbit's commercial spyware, PC Surveillance System (PSS), renamed PC 360.</p>
