<h2 id="cyberpoint">CyberPoint</h2>
<p>CyberPoint is listed as a partner to Hacking Team, the Italian company that sold spyware used by repressive regimes across the world. It also has a known presence in Abu Dhabi, UAE, and trains analysts with the Electronic Security Authority, the Emirati intelligence agency.</p>
