<h2 id="damiba-group">Damiba Group</h2>
<p>Damiba Group is a Serbian company producing AI-powered drones and radar systems. According to a report by the Border Violence Monitoring Network, it has been involved in supplying unmanned aerial vehicles and other surveillance equipment in a project jointly managed by the EU Commission and the International Organization for Migration (IOM).</p>
