<h2 id="darkowl">DarkOwl</h2>
<p>DarkOwl is a cybersecurity company providing tools for dark web intelligence and monitoring. Their platform provides access to a vast database of dark web content, enabling clients to search for leaked credentials, sensitive data, and other details. Its DarkOwl Vision UI has access to a wide range of sources including Tor and Telegram. It also has capabilities for entity-based searches for specific variables like email addresses, IPs, and cryptocurrencies, as well as network-specific filtering to focus on particular darknet platforms, forums or messaging services. Its Dubai-based subsidiary is DarkOwl FZE LLC, which it uses to support intelligence operations by the United Arab Emirates and other governments in the region.</p>
