<h2 id="dat-con">Dat-Con</h2>
<p>Dat-Con is a Slovenian company providing Mobile Surveillance Systems (MSS) to Frontex, the European Border and Coast Guard Agency. These systems are used for border surveillance and monitoring operations.</p>
