<h2 id="datastream-group">Datastream Group</h2>
<p>Datastream Group, an American data broker, aggregates and sells large amounts of geolocated personal data, often collected through mobile apps. An investigation revealed that Datastream Group's database includes information on over 47 million individuals, such as GPS coordinates, device details, and app usage patterns.</p>
<p>The company collects geolocation data from 137 countries, as revealed in a dataset tied to its activities.</p>
