<h2 id="dcx-systems">DCX Systems</h2>
<p>DCX Systems provides a range of surveillance technologies, including surveillance radars, electro-optic devices, signal analyzers and unmanned aerial drones. The company has established itself as a key Indian Offset Partner (IOP) for international defense companies, especially Israel Aerospace Industries (IAI) and its subsidiary ELTA Systems Limited. It also owns two subsidiaries in Israel.</p>
