<h2 id="eaglemsgspy">EagleMsgSpy</h2>
<p>EagleMsgSpy is a mobile surveillance tool for Android and iOS devices developed by Wuhan Chinasoft Token InfoTech Co., Ltd. Since 2017, it has been deployed by police across multiple Chinese provinces to collect SMS, audio, and geolocation data. Despite its widespread use, the company remained under the radar until its spyware activities were publicly exposed in December 2024.</p>
