<h2 id="echodyne">Echodyne</h2>
<p>Echodyne is a company that develops compact, high-performance radar systems powered by its proprietary Metamaterial Electronically Scanning Array (MESA) technology. The company’s radar is used in drone surveillance, border security, and perimeter monitoring. Its technology has been adopted by U.S. federal agencies, including Customs and Border Protection (CBP), for surveillance operations along the U.S.-Mexico border.</p>
