<h2 id="ekin">Ekin</h2>
<p>Ekin Technology, a Turkish firm, is a developer of AI-driven smart city surveillance systems, including facial recognition and license plate recognition (LPR). Their products, such as the Ekin Patrol G2 and Ekin Spotter, integrate multiple surveillance functions into mobile and fixed platforms. These systems are designed for real-time data analysis and centralized control via their Red Eagle operating system.</p>
