<h2 id="elbit-industries">Elbit Industries</h2>
<p>Elbit Systems is a leading military tech exporter in Israel, specializing in various advanced surveillance technologies, deployed in space, air, sea and ground operations. Its surveillance systems, drones, and other high-tech tools, which are used in violent military operations and in high demand worldwide.</p>
