<h2 id="elm">Elm</h2>
<p>Elm is a Saudi government-owned technology company operating under the Public Investment Fund (PIF). The entity develops and manages platforms that facilitate state surveillance. These include systems for biometric identification, digital identity, predictive analytics, and population tracking through integrated government databases. Elm has built platforms for border control and law enforcement analytics, and has contracts with the country's Ministry of Interior.</p>
