<h2 id="european-sao">European SAO</h2>
<p>European SAO is a Malta-based company contracted by Frontex, the European Border and Coast Guard Agency, for aerial surveillance. It is a sister company of DEA Aviation (UK), which has worked extensively with Frontex by providing airborne surveillance equipments. This relationship enables European SAO to bypass Brexit-related restrictions that prevent UK-based companies from participating in certain EU contracts.</p>
