<h2 id="fly4less">Fly4Less</h2>
<p>Fly4Less, a Hungary-based company, is a contractor for Frontex, the European Border and Coast Guard Agency, to provide aerial surveillance services. The company operates aircraft equipped with advanced monitoring systems for border control, targeting migrants.</p>
