<h2 id="forsolution">Forsolution</h2>
<p>Forsolution, a Czech-based company, is a developer of surveillance and monitoring equipment. Its primary product, the DELTA wireless digital audio monitoring system, is used for monitoring individuals under house arrest. The company's tools are specifically designed for covert operations and are used by police, intelligence agencies, special forces, and other government-approved organizations. Their products are also often showcased at international exhibitions and arms fairs targeting global markets.</p>
