<h2 id="gatewatcher">Gatewatcher</h2>
<p>Gatewatcher is a cybersecurity firm specializing in advanced threat detection and network surveillance. Its tools, like Trackwatch, use machine learning and behavioral analysis to monitor and analyze network behavior.</p>
<p>In 2024, Gatewatcher strengthened its collaboration with Saudi Arabia as part of the Franco-Saudi partnership on cybersecurity. The company provides advanced multi-vector detection technologies to the Saudi government.</p>
<p>Gatewatcher has also been embroiled in controversy due to legal allegations against its founder, Philippe Gillet, who has been accused of hacking and orchestrating violent attacks amid a dispute with former business partner Franck Berezay.</p>
