<h2 id="general-robotics">General Robotics</h2>
<p>General Robotics Ltd. (GRL), based in Hod Hasharon, Israel, specializes in developing advanced robotic systems for military and defense applications. One of its products, "Pitbull", can be mounted on various platforms for remote surveillance activities. It was acquired in March, 2022 by the American company Sig Sauer, one of the world's leading arms, ammunition, and optical sights companies.</p>
