<h2 id="genieo-innovation">Genieo Innovation</h2>
<p>Genieo Innovation, formerly called Anabel Software, is an Israeli company that specializes in developing software often categorized as adware, grayware or malware. In 2014, Genieo was acquired by Somoto for $34 million.</p>
