<h2 id="geoai">GEOAI</h2>
<p>GEOAI, also known as Guangzhou ImapCloud Intelligent Technology Co., Ltd., develops drone docking stations, edge computing modules, and AI-powered sensors to create integrated sky-to-ground monitoring systems. The company utilized Nvidia chips for its gait recognition technology that could identify individuals by their walking patterns.</p>
