<h2 id="giza-systems">Giza Systems</h2>
<p>Giza Systems is a partner of Nexign, formerly known as Peter-Service, a Russian company that specializes in providing software and services for telecommunications companies. According to its website, Nexign’s products have been delivered to 12 countries and includes the surveillance company Protei as a partner. In a press release, data collection is listed as one of the services that will be provided as part of the partnership between Giza Systems and Nexign.</p>
