<h2 id="graylark">Graylark</h2>
<p>Graylark Technologies is the developer of a tool called GeoSpy. According to 404 Media, GeoSpy is a powerful AI tool capable of geolocating photos within seconds by analyzing features such as vegetation, architecture, and building distances. Initially accessible to the public, the tool has since been restricted to law enforcement and government agencies after its misuse for stalking. GeoSpy claims to have the ability to simplify complex geolocation tasks that typically require years of expertise, making it accessible to users with minimal training.</p>
