<h2 id="hakluyt">Hakluyt</h2>
<p>Hakluyt &amp; Company is a London-based intelligence agency known for its discreet operations and high-level clientele, including multinational corporations and governments. The firm is notable for its ties to the intelligence community, as it is staffed predominantly by former officers from agencies such as MI6, the CIA, and other elite intelligence organizations. </p>
<p>In 2001, BP and Shell were called out for hiring Hakluyt to spy on Greenpeace activists.</p>
<p>In 2021, Hakluyt opened a subsidiary in Dubai called Hakluyt &amp; Company (Middle East) FZE.</p>
