<h2 id="hisilicon">HiSilicon</h2>
<p>HiSilicon is a subsidiary of China’s Huawei Technologies Co. Ltd. which sells chips with advanced capabilities for surveillance cameras. It is one of the world’s most dominant chipmaker in the surveillance camera industry.</p>
