<h2 id="hocell">Hocell</h2>
<p>Hocell is a company that provides surveillance tools, including a Drone-Mounted IMSI Catcher, a Portable IMSI Catcher and a Vehicle-Mounted IMSI Catcher, that can search and track cell phones as well as locate targets by identifying their IMSI numbers. The company is headquartered in Shenzhen, China.</p>
