<h2 id="indra-sistemas">Indra Sistemas</h2>
<p>Indra has been involved in providing surveillance and border control technologies that have been used in discriminatory practices, particularly in regions with stringent controls on migration and dissent. It is a provider of drones equipped with sensors, cameras, radars, AI and communication systems to monitor and control borders, as well as for intelligence gathering and target tracking.</p>
