<h2 id="inex-technologies">Inex Technologies</h2>
<p>Inex Technologies provides Automated License Plate Recognition (ALPR) systems for law enforcement agencies. Their cameras use neural network-based video analytics to process images on-board and output license plate numbers, reference images, and confidence scores. According to the company, this AI-powered processing enables real-time analysis at 40 FPS in their mobile systems, allowing for immediate identification and alerts on watchlisted vehicles. In 2006, Inex Technologies acquired Zamir Recognition Systems. They rebranded as INEX/ZAMIR while operating from headquarters in both Israel and the U.S, but the company currently goes by the name Inex Technologies.</p>
