<h2 id="infinova">Infinova</h2>
<p>Infinova Corporation, headquartered in Monmouth Junction, New Jersey, is a global provider of advanced surveillance technologies, including CCTV systems, IP cameras, facial recognition systems, deep-learning algorithms, multi-angle recognition and AI-driven analytics. It's heavily involved in China's expansive surveillance programs, such as the "Sharp Eyes" platform and projects in regions like Xinjiang to target Uyghurs. Infinova deleted all articles about its Xinjiang projects from its Chinese website, though IPVM (The Authority On Physical Security Technology) retained copies.</p>
<p>Infinova has also been involved in major mass surveillance projects globally, including in countries like Kuwait, Saudi Arabia, Turkey, Mexico, India and the UAE.</p>
