<h2 id="inpedio">Inpedio</h2>
<p>Inpedio received millions in investments from the Israel Aerospace Industries (IAI.) IAI made the investment through its Singaporian subsidiary, Custodio PTE. According to Haaretz, employeers at Inpedia were involved in developing Predator in Cytrox offices. Inpedio was registered in the Netherlands in 2016 by Rotem Farkash and Abraham Rubinstein, who also established Cytrox Holdings in Hungary.</p>
