<h2 id="inreach">InReach</h2>
<p>InReach was set up as a business entity in Cyprus for the sole purpose of promoting QuaDream’s surveillance products outside of Israel. QuaDream is an Israeli company that specializes in the development and sale of advanced digital offensive technology to government clients. The company is known for its spyware marketed under the name “Reign”, which, like NSO Group’s Pegasus spyware, reportedly utilizes zero-click exploits to hack into target devices.</p>
