<h2 id="intecs">Intecs</h2>
<p>Intecs GmbH is a provider of surveillance and intelligence gathering technologies tailored for government and police agencies. Their product offerings include digital audio surveillance tools with data processing, monitoring solutions for cellular and satellite data, and video surveillance systems with high-speed transmission capabilities using RF, cellular, and IP-based technologies.</p>
