<h2 id="intellifusion">Intellifusion</h2>
<p>Intellifusion is an AI vision company whose "DeepEye" platform provides non‑cooperative facial recognition and large‑scale video deployments. The platform's capabilities include face recognition cameras, visual analysis engines, structured recognition engines, and police mobile terminals. The company was founded in 2014 and based in Shenzhen.</p>
