<h2 id="iproov">iProov</h2>
<p>iProov is a biometric technology company that develops facial recognition software. The U.S. Department of Homeland Security (DHS) and Frontex (the European Border and Coast Guard Agency) have adopted iProov's tools for use on borders. iProov's systems claim to utilize advanced AI to perform liveness detection as part of their verification process.</p>
