<h2 id="ipsotek">Ipsotek</h2>
<p>Ipsotek, an Eviden business, provides AI-powered video analytics for law enforcement agencies. Its platform, VISuite AI, enables real-time detection of events while performing facial recognition, license plate recognition, and crowd monitoring. The patented “Tag and Track” system allows police to follow individuals or vehicles across multiple camera feeds. The company claims its products are widely adopted by police agencies worldwide.</p>
<p>In 2021, it was acquired by Atos, a multinational information technology (IT) service and consulting company headquartered in France.</p>
