<h2 id="iristar">Iristar</h2>
<p>Iristar is a Chinese company that develops facial and iris recognition technologies, with strong ties to China's government. According to Intelligence Online, it collaborates with other major Chinese tech and surveillance firms like Huawei, Hanwang and Megvii.</p>
