<h2 id="iteco">iTeco</h2>
<p>iTeco is a Russian IT company that has developed surveillance technologies compatible with Russia's System for Operative Investigative Activities (SORM). iTeco's information analysis system, Xfiles, has been utilized by Russian security services to monitor online sources, including media outlets, blogs, forums and social networks. This system helps automate the collection and analysis of online content, allowing authorities to track and identify dissenting material.</p>
