<h2 id="jenoptik">Jenoptik</h2>
<p>Jenoptik is the German company behind TraffiCatch, a mass surveillance tool designed to capture Bluetooth and wireless signals emitted by everyday devices, including smartphones, smartwatches, earbuds, and car entertainment systems. Recently deployed at the U.S. border, this tool enables real-time tracking of individuals by associating wireless signals with vehicles identified through license plate readers.</p>
