<h2 id="johnson-controls">Johnson Controls</h2>
<p>Johnson Controls is a provider of video surveillance technologies. Its portfolio includes IP and analog cameras paired with intelligent DVRs and NVRs that record, analyze, and manage footage in real time. They power the facial recognition technology installed in the subway in São Paulo, Brazil. They also supply the facial recognition technology at the BEEAH Headquarters in Sharjah, United Arab Emirates, which claims to be the first fully AI-integrated building in the Middle East. They currently operate in more than 150 countries.</p>
