<h2 id="kavit">Kavit</h2>
<p>Kavit Electronics Industries Ltd, based in Israel, is a developer and distributor of electronic surveillance and communication interception technologies. Their products include IMSI catchers, which are used to intercept mobile communications, track devices, and gather intelligence.</p>
<p>According to its official website, the company's clients include the Israeli Security Services, Brazilian Police, Mexican Army, Nigerian Air Force, United Kingdom Ministry of Defense, US Police, Spanish Police, Italian Air Force, Royal Thai Army, and South Korean Military.</p>
