<h2 id="kickboard">Kickboard</h2>
<p>Kickboard, a company acquired by PowerSchool, gathers data on students' behavior and social-emotional skills. This platform allows schools to track and analyze behavioral trends, disciplinary actions, and emotional development. As part of PowerSchool's suite of tools, Kickboard integrates this data with broader analytics, such as predictive risk scoring, detailed student profiles and other forms of student monitoring.</p>
