<h2 id="killer-mobile">Killer Mobile</h2>
<p>Killer Mobile is a Las Vegas-based company that develops spyware tools marketed for both consumer and government use. Its products include Tracer, a call recording and tracking app, and FoxPhone, a tool designed for covert surveillance. </p>
<p>According to a Forbes investigation, Killer Mobile's cellphone surveillance tools were redistributed by Moscow-based tech dealer OpenGSM, which caters to both government agencies and everyday consumers.</p>
