<h2 id="knightscope">Knightscope</h2>
<p>Knightscope is a developer of Autonomous Security Robots (ASRs) that are equipped with facial recognition capabilities, Automatic License Plate Recognition (ALPR), and smartphone signal detection. The company claims their robots provide 360-degree high-definition surveillance, capturing continuous video footage that can be analyzed with AI.</p>
