<h2 id="krikel">Krikel</h2>
<p>Krikel is a preferred supplier of surveillance and spyware tools to the Greek law enforcement and security authorities. It supplied Cytrox's Predator spyware to Greece. It is also the Greek representative of RCS Lab, an Italian company selling surveillance software.</p>
