<h2 id="lenslock">LensLock</h2>
<p>LensLock is a law enforcement technology company that distributes surveillance products, such as high-resolution surveillance cameras integrated with cloud infrastructure and AI-powered visual and audio identification systems. LensLock has partnered with PlateSmart to offer Automated License Plate Recognition (ALPR) technology for use by police agencies.</p>
