<h2 id="leo-impact">Leo Impact</h2>
<p>Leo Impact is an Indian cyber intelligence firm based in Rajasthan, developing both defensive and offensive cybersecurity technologies. Leo Impact has also been linked to controversial surveillance activities. Its now-defunct website, "SpyPhoneWorld.com," openly marketed surveillance software capable of remotely monitoring phones, targeting use cases like tracking partners or employees.</p>
