<h2 id="leon-technology">Leon Technology</h2>
<p>Leon Technology Company Limited (Leon Technology) is one of the key companies that helped the PRC build the Integrated Joint Operations Platform, a surveillance system in Xinjiang. Leon Technology has multiple surveillance project contracts with the PRC, particularly in parts of the country with sizeable ethnic minority populations.</p>
