<h2 id="leonardo">Leonardo</h2>
<p>Leonardo S.p.A. is an Italian defense company that provides various surveillance technologies across multiple domains, including air, land, sea, and space, primarily for military and government operations. Its portfolio includes mobile surveillance systems, which combine radar sensors, optronics, and command-and-control facilities for real-time monitoring. Their electro-optical and infrared systems enable tracking of medium- to long-range targets. It's also a developer of airborne mission management systems, such as ATOS, which integrates multiple sensors for surveillance purposes.</p>
