<h2 id="liferaft">LifeRaft</h2>
<p>LifeRaft is a social media intelligence company that provides tools for monitoring and analyzing online activity. Its platform is designed to scan large volumes of public social media posts, identify potential risks, and provide related intelligence. LifeRaft's technology has been tested by organizations like the Fresno Police Department in California, USA for social media surveillance purposes.</p>
