<h2 id="lightspeed">Lightspeed</h2>
<p>Lightspeed Systems develops tools designed to monitor and manage student activity on school-issued devices. Its software provides features like real-time screen monitoring, web filtering, and AI-powered alerts to identify "inappropriate behavior." The software can track students' online activities both during and outside school hours, often without their explicit awareness. The company claims to be used on 15 million student devices globally, and by 28,000 schools worldwide.</p>
