<h2 id="logic-industries">Logic Industries</h2>
<p>Logic Industries is an affiliate of AGT International (Asia Global Technologies), which partners closely with the government of the United Arab Emirates to provide a wide range of mass surveillance equipment.</p>
<details class="tip">
<summary>Internal MISP references</summary>
