<h2 id="logically">Logically</h2>
<p>Logically, a UK-based artificial intelligence company, has been involved in government contracts for monitoring and analyzing social media content. The company has received over £1.2 million in funding from the UK government to identify and flag specific content online it deems to be misinformation or disinformation. Using AI, Logically processes data from hundreds of thousands of media sources and public posts on major social media platforms.</p>
<p>Logically's tools were initially tested during elections in India and later expanded to support other government efforts. In the United States, the Washington Secretary of State extended a contract with Logically to monitor social media posts concerning elections. The Wall Street Journal reported in 2021 that the Department of Homeland Security (DHS) had engaged in at least preliminary discussions with Logically.</p>
