<h2 id="macchina-security">Macchina Security</h2>
<p>Macchina Security is a Belgrade-based firm that imports Chinese technology into Serbia and has been awarded contracts to supply public video surveillance and traffic monitoring systems to numerous municipalities.</p>
<p>A 2023 investigation revealed that approximately one-third of local governments in Serbia utilize surveillance systems acquired from Chinese manufacturers like Dahua and Hikvision through Macchina Security.</p>
