<h2 id="masl">MASL</h2>
<p>MASL (Millennium Automation Systems Limited, and formerly known as MAPL World) is a technology company that provides surveillance and smart city products. For the Delhi Police, MASL implemented a citywide surveillance system that uses Facial Recognition Systems (FRS) and Automatic License Plate Recognition (ALPR). The system is integrated with video analytics and a centralized command center designed for policing efforts.</p>
