<h2 id="medialogia">Medialogia</h2>
<p>Medialogia is a Russian technology company that develops tools for online and social media monitoring. It has developed systems such as the "Blog Monitoring System" and "Prisma," which are utilized by Russian authorities to track and analyze online content, including blogs and social networks. In April 2025, the National Media Group (NMG) announced plans to acquire Medialogia.</p>
