<h2 id="movia">Movia</h2>
<p>Movia S.p.A., an Italian cyber intelligence company, develops spyware tools, such as "Spyder," which is used for telecommunication, environmental, and telematic interceptions.  The company collaborates with Italian prosecution offices and law enforcement agencies, providing end-to-end monitoring solutions.</p>
<p>Movia showcased its Spyder spyware at ISS World in Dubai in 2023, an intelligence trade show which it also sponsored.</p>
