<h2 id="network-solutions">Network Solutions</h2>
<p>Network Solutions (Сетевые Решения) is a Russian software developer that provides billing systems for telecommunications operators. Beyond its billing solutions, the company provides tools for transferring data to SORM (System for Operative Investigative Activities), a Russian government-mandated surveillance system. According to its website, Network Solutions facilitates the direct transfer of sensitive subscriber data to SORM from certified billing systems. This data includes call and payment information, personal customer details, accurate addresses, passport information of individuals, and details of legal entities.</p>
