<h2 id="nexign">Nexign</h2>
<p>Nexign, formerly known as Peter-Service, is a Russian company that provides surveillance software and monitoring services for telecommunications companies. The company is part of USM Telecom, owned by Kremlin insider Alisher Usmanov.</p>
<p>According to its website, Nexign’s products have been delivered to 12 countries and includes the surveillance company Protei as a partner.</p>
