<h2 id="oniks-line">Oniks-Line</h2>
<p>Oniks-Line is a Russian company that develops surveillance and interception technology, particularly systems used for state monitoring and data interception. It is one of the providers of SORM (System for Operational-Investigative Activities) equipment, a surveillance framework widely used in Russia and exported to other countries.</p>
<p>In Kyrgyzstan, Oniks-Line's SORM technology has been implemented to allow authorities to intercept and monitor communications.</p>
