<h2 id="opticoelectron">Opticoelectron</h2>
<p>Opticoelectron Group JSCo is a Bulgarian developer and distributor of optical and surveillance technologies. Its offerings include Mobile Surveillance Systems (MSS), such as the MUSON series, which feature high-resolution day and night cameras, thermal imaging, and long-range capabilities for monitoring. Opticoelectron collaborates with international organizations, including Frontex, the European Border and Coast Guard Agency, to provide surveillance equipment for border control.</p>
