<h2 id="osi-systems">OSI Systems</h2>
<p>OSI Systems is a global provider of security screening and optoelectronics products. Through its subsidiaries, including Rapiscan Systems and Gatekeeper Intelligent Security, OSI Systems develops and deploys surveillance technologies. This includes imaging and sensor technologies to provide real-time, automated vehicle inspections and facial recognition tools, often for use at borders and "smart city" surveillance projects such as ones in Saudi Arabia and the UAE.</p>
