<h2 id="pavo-group">Pavo Group</h2>
<p>Pavo Group is a Turkish company providing interception and threat intelligence services through its subsidiaries, such as InterProbe and Interdata, serving both military and government clients globally. Its capabilities include IMSI-catcher technology, exploiting undisclosed software vulnerabilities for intelligence purposes, cyber intelligence systems including data interception, and technologies for tracking and locating mobile devices.</p>
<p>Barzan Holdings, the strategic investment arm of Qatar's Ministry of Defense and the commercial gateway for the country's military defense industry, owns a stake in the company.</p>
