<h2 id="peekyou">PeekYou</h2>
<p>PeekYou is a U.S.-based people-search engine founded in 2006 that aggregates publicly available personal info, such as your name, age, location, links to social media profiles (from sources that include Facebook, LinkedIn, Twitter/X, Instagram, TikTok), blogs, and maps out possible relatives, with all data curated into searchable profiles. The company had applied for a patent for a method that matches people's real names to the pseudonyms they use on social media, blogs and other websites.</p>
