<h2 id="phoenix-worldwide-industries">Phoenix Worldwide Industries</h2>
<p>Phoenix Worldwide Industries is a U.S defense contractor that supplied Venezuela's government with Triggerfish devices, a specific type of IMSI Catcher in 2001. The firm also works closely with U.S. government intelligence agencies.</p>
