<h2 id="polus-tech">Polus Tech</h2>
<p>Polus Tech is a Swiss-based company that develops and distributes surveillance technology, including IMSI catchers, which are devices capable of intercepting and tracking mobile phone communications. The company is led by Niv Karmi, a former co-founder of NSO Group.</p>
<p>In 2020, Polus Tech exported surveillance equipment worth 2.2 million Swiss francs to Indonesia.</p>
