<h2 id="portaone">PortaOne</h2>
<p>PortaOne is a Canadian software company that specializes in developing products for telecommunication service providers. A report by Citizen Lab revealed that it was selected by Iranian cellular carrier, Ariantel, to provide mobile account creation, service provisioning, and customized integration with Iran's Legal Intercept system, a component for conducting usage surveillance and control activity.</p>
