<h2 id="positive-technologies">Positive Technologies</h2>
<p>Positive Technologies is a Russian cybersecurity firm valued at over $1 billion, and which is reportedly involved in surveillance and spyware activities. The company provides network security solutions to businesses, governments, and international clients, while collaborating with Russian intelligence agencies like the FSB and GRU. In 2023, Russia's digital ministry, along with major local tech companies including Positive Technologies, met with Iran’s communications and technology ministry to discuss exporting Russian technology to Iran.</p>
