<h2 id="predicio">Predicio</h2>
<p>Predicio is a France-based company and provider of location data tracking and analytics. It collects granular location data by paying app developers for access to user data through its software development kit (SDK) called "Telescope." This data is then sold to various clients, including government agencies and private organizations. Reports indicate that Predicio's data has been part of a supply chain used by contractors working with U.S government contractors that service U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement (ICE) and the FBI.</p>
