<h2 id="pro4sec">PRO4SEC</h2>
<p>PRO4SEC is a Croatia-based manufacturer that provides covert surveillance technologies tailored for military, federal, and national intelligence operations. The company uses Surface-Mount Device (SMD) technology for their surveillance equipment. PRO4SEC operates exclusively through government-certified resellers and claims to have 41 resellers across 58 countries.</p>
