<h2 id="protect-electronic-systems">Protect Electronic Systems</h2>
<p>Protect Electronic Systems is a company based in the United Arab Emirates. It is one of the spyware firms detected by Google and Meta, and the company claims to be a cybersecurity firm but works with Variston, another spyware vendor, to package its spyware into products sold to government customers.</p>
