<h2 id="protei">Protei</h2>
<p>Protei is a Russia-based company that offers an extensive suite of telecommunications technologies with significant surveillance capabilities, enabling the monitoring of user communications, locations, and behaviors. Protei equipment is used by a range of telecom companies worldwide for logging internet usage as well as for blocking websites. It also offers "Smart City" related technologies for mass surveillance purposes. The company has offices in Jordan and Estonia and partners with major firms including Nokia and Oracle.</p>
