<h2 id="q-cyber-technologies">Q Cyber Technologies</h2>
<p>Q Cyber Technologies SARL is one of the entities affiliated with NSO Group, an Israeli-based company that sells Pegasus, one of the world’s most sophisticated hacking tools, to governments and law enforcement agencies. The abuses were detailed in the Pegasus Project, a collaborative investigation by media organizations and Amnesty International revealing widespread misuse of Pegasus in multiple countries, targeting thousands of individuals. Q Cyber Technologies signs contracts, issues invoices, and receives payments from NSO Group customers.</p>
