<h2 id="raviraj-technologies">Raviraj Technologies</h2>
<p>Raviraj Technologies is an Indian company based in Pune that develops and distributes RFID and biometric technology to a range of countries worldwide. Its products include facial recognition software, fingerprint and palm vein scanners and iris recognition systems.</p>
