<h2 id="rebsec-solutions">Rebsec Solutions</h2>
<p>Rebsec Solutions is a "hack-for-hire" group targeting sectors like government, healthcare, and telecom in countries such as Saudi Arabia, the UAE, and Bahrain. Their campaigns reportedly involve spear-phishing and credential-stealing tactics. Google identified Rebsec Solutions as part of a group conducting malicious campaigns against targeted individuals.</p>
