<h2 id="robotican">Robotican</h2>
<p>Robotican develops unmanned autonomous robots. One of its primary products, Rooster, is a versatile robotic drone utilized by the Israeli military in Gaza for intelligence gathering and surveillance. Additionally, it has gained adoption by various militaries worldwide for similar applications. Its Gallo system, designed for reconnaissance in confined spaces such as tunnels and buildings, has been delivered to the U.S. Special Operations Command (USSOCOM). It features advanced MESH communication for simultaneous operation of multiple units in communication-denied environments.</p>
