<h2 id="salvationdata">SalvationDATA</h2>
<p>SalvationDATA, which also operates under the name XLY Technology, is a Chinese company that develops digital forensics and data recovery technologies, providing tools primarily for law enforcement and intelligence agencies. The company's products are able to extract, analyze, and recover data from various digital devices, including mobile phones, computers, and storage systems.</p>
<p>SalvationDATA has established partnerships with security and intelligence agencies in multiple countries, including Myanmar, where it has provided forensic systems to assist in data analysis and surveillance operations.</p>
