<h2 id="scl-group">SCL Group</h2>
<p>The SCL Group, formerly known as Strategic Communication Laboratories, gained notoriety primarily through its subsidiary, Cambridge Analytica. SCL Group and Cambridge Analytica were involved in various activities related to data collection, unauthorized access to personal data, and influence/manipulation campaigns. The data was collected from Facebook through an app called thisisyourdigitallife.</p>
