<h2 id="scylla">Scylla</h2>
<p>Scylla is an AI-powered surveillance system that claims to be capable of detecting and classifying human features and behaviors in real time. It has been tested by the U.S. Department of Defense at military installations.</p>
<p>Scylla's surveillance products are used by a variety of industries beyond the military. These include private security companies, corporate facilities, retail businesses, educational institutions, and public venues like stadiums and airports.</p>
