<h2 id="sensetime">SenseTime</h2>
<p>SenseTime is a leading Chinese AI company specializing in facial recognition and computer vision technologies. Their advanced algorithms enable real-time detection of faces and objects. It has been under scrutiny for its role in Uyghur surveillance.</p>
