<h2 id="sinovatio">Sinovatio</h2>
<p>Sinovatio is a Chinese company that develops and deploys various surveillance technologies. The company creates high-tech solutions for video surveillance, facial recognition, and AI-powered monitoring systems, including incorporating AI to enhance the capabilities of traditional CCTV networks.</p>
