<h2 id="sio">SIO</h2>
<p>SIO is an Italian spyware company that distributes malicious Android apps designed to steal private user data. The spyware, known as "Spyrtacus," was used to target individuals by masquerading as legitimate applications, like WhatsApp.</p>
