<h2 id="smartware">Smartware</h2>
<p>Smartware was a Russian surveillance technology provider that developed the Random Information Collection System (KRIT), a tool used by Russia's Ministry of Internal Affairs to closely monitor online discussions, news coverage, and social media activity.</p>
