<h2 id="sosi">SOSi</h2>
<p>SOS International LLC (SOSi) is a company that helps government agencies track down people. In October 2025, ICE contracted SOSi for $7 million to perform "skip tracing services", essentially locating individuals who are difficult to find. The company employs image recognition technology that can match faces and license plates to databases, which includes facial recognition capabilities.</p>
<p>SOSi operates internationally. The company is headquartered in Reston, Virginia, but maintains offices and customer engagements in at least 40 countries worldwide.</p>
