<h2 id="speck-systems">Speck Systems</h2>
<p>Speck Systems Limited is an Indian company that develops aerial surveillance systems and defense technologies. The company provides advanced tools for mapping, remote sensing, and geographic information systems (GIS) primarily for defense and law enforcement applications.</p>
<p>The company has been involved in collaborations with international partners, including Israel Aerospace Industries (IAI), to develop and supply unmanned aerial vehicles (UAVs).</p>
<p>In 2025, it was acquired by Bondada Engineering.</p>
