<h2 id="spireon">Spireon</h2>
<p>Spireon is a provider of vehicle intelligence solutions, and has been providing location and telematics data to U.S. immigration enforcement agencies, including Immigration and Customs Enforcement (ICE) and Customs and Border Protection (CBP). These agencies have utilized data from Spireon's GPS tracking systems to monitor vehicle movements. In February 2022, Solera Holdings, a global provider of vehicle lifecycle and fleet management software, announced its acquisition of Spireon.</p>
