<h2 id="stellar-technologies">Stellar Technologies</h2>
<p>Stellar Technologies is a developer of surveillance and artificial intelligence tools. One of its primary products is NesherAI, a facial recognition tool capable of identifying individuals even when they are wearing masks. This tool has been utilized by private groups and organizations to identify participants in protests, specifically pro-Palestine activists, students, and faculty. It has been employed to assist in reporting foreign students and activists to U.S agencies such as ICE, leading to visa revocations and deportations. </p>
<p>The company's other tools include CyberBird, claiming to offer "revolutionary surveillance."</p>
