<h2 id="supercom">SuperCom</h2>
<p>SuperCom is an Israeli company that develops electronic monitoring and digital identity technologies. Its core product, the PureSecurity Suite, provides tools for public monitoring, including GPS tracking, home detention compliance, and individualized case management. </p>
<p>SuperCom's surveillance tools have been highlighted for their role in militarizing campus police forces in the U.S., where they are reportedly used to monitor and suppress student protests.</p>
