<h2 id="syborg">Syborg</h2>
<p>Syborg is a German-based provider of intelligence solutions, specifically data mining, surveillance, and lawful interception technologies. Its capabilities include Wi-Fi interception, enabling the collection, decoding, and analysis of network traffic, and telecommunications interception systems that monitor and analyze voice and data communications. </p>
<p>The company was acquired by the Israeli surveillance firm Verint in 2000.</p>
