<h2 id="synergy-telematics">Synergy Telematics</h2>
<p>Synergy Telematics Pvt. Ltd, AKA Synergy, an India-based company that develops AI-powered surveillance technologies. Synergy's AI-supported surveillance systems were adopted at large-scale events like the Kumbh Mela for realtime crowd monitoring. The company collaborates closely with police agencies in India.</p>
