<h2 id="systools">SysTools</h2>
<p>SysTools is a provider of digital forensic technologies. They also offer training programs tailored primarily for law enforcement agencies. Their email forensics tools like MailXaminer supports over 80 email clients. The company also develops workplace monitoring tools.</p>
