<h2 id="sz-dji">SZ DJI</h2>
<p>SZ DJI Technology Co., Ltd. (SZ DJI) has provided drones to the Xinjiang Public Security Bureau, which are used to surveil and target Uyghurs, Kazakh, and Kyrgyz people. The company is a major supplier of camera drones and other products to 43 countries globally, including the US, UK, and Australia. It also sold drones to the Serbian government. Key investors include Accel and Sequoia Capital.</p>
