<h2 id="tactic-labs">Tactic Labs</h2>
<p>Tactic Labs, a subsidiary of the Avnon Group, is a developer of interception technologies, including IMSI-catchers and WiFi interceptors. A key offering is their Wi-Fi sniffer, an untraceable device that grants access to nearby Wi-Fi networks, cellular devices, and computers, allowing operators to collect private user data.</p>
