<h2 id="tekever">Tekever</h2>
<p>Tekever is a provider of surveillance drones and unmanned aerial systems (UAS) for monitoring operations. The company’s drones are equipped with artificial intelligence (AI) capabilities, enabling real-time data analysis, and its drones are designed for diverse surveillance missions, including border control. Tekever’s drones have been widely used in Frontex (EU border agency) operations and by several national coast guards and defense ministries.</p>
