<h2 id="tekhargos">TekhArgos</h2>
<p>TekhArgos, established in 2009, is a company that develops, produces and deploys SORM (System for Operative Investigative Activities) equipment. SORM is a surveillance system used by Russian and CIS telecommunications operators to enable state-mandated monitoring of communications. Since 2018, TekhArgos has been part of Citadel, a prominent company servicing Russia's telecommunications surveillance industry. It is now part of Garda Telekom Гарда Телеком).</p>
