<h2 id="telekonta">Telekonta</h2>
<p>Telekonta is a Lithuanian company that develops video surveillance technology. The company recently secured a contract to develop and implement a surveillance system along the Lithuania-Belarus border, targeting migrants. </p>
<p>In collaboration with the Israeli company Elbit, Telekonta has also carried out the installation of VSAT surveillance equipment for the Baltic Sea border.</p>
