<h2 id="thetabyte">ThetaByte</h2>
<p>ThetaByte, registered in Lithuania and founded and headed by Israeli businessman Shay Tal, created the WebMine2Go platform, a tool designed to gather data from social networks as well as the clear web, deep web, and dark web, analyzing it to uncover connections. The company offers more advanced services, including tactical communication interception, to monitor the activities of online targets.</p>
