<h2 id="tracespan">TraceSpan</h2>
<p>TraceSpan Communications is a developer of monitoring and interception technologies for broadband access networks. Its GPON Phantom series provide passive monitoring solutions. These systems are designed for use by law enforcement agencies to capture and analyze data from networks like VDSL, GPON, and DOCSIS.</p>
