<h2 id="uav-tactical-systems-ltd">UAV Tactical Systems Ltd</h2>
<p>A joint venture company, UAV Tactical Systems Ltd (U-TacS), based in Leicester, has been set up by Thales UK and Elbit to produce the Watchkeeper system in the UK. The Watchkeeper UAV provides intelligence, surveillance, target acquisition and reconnaissance (ISTAR) capability to the UK armed forces. Reports show that it has been field-tested on Palestinians in collaboration with the Israeli government.</p>
