<h2 id="unisys">Unisys</h2>
<p>Unisys is a multinational IT and consulting company that works closely with the U.S Customs and Border Protection (CBP) and Immigration and Customs Enforcement (ICE). In 2016, CBP gave Unisys a $229.7 million contract to implement biometric checks at U.S. entry and exit points. Unisys has also helped deploy license plate readers and RFID technology to monitor vehicles and verify travelers' identities.</p>
