<h2 id="utx-technologies">UTX Technologies</h2>
<p>UTX provides mobile device tracking software. It's based in Cyprus and is also registered in Lithuania. It was acquired by surveillance giant Verint in 2014. It is now considered a Cognyte subsidiary.</p>
