<h2 id="vehant-technologies">Vehant Technologies</h2>
<p>Vehant Technologies is a provider of AI-driven surveillance technologies, offering advanced systems for monitoring to law enforcement agencies. It was founded in 2005 at IIT Delhi. Its capabilities include video analytics, intelligent monitoring, and AI-powered tools for smart cities. Vehant works closely with police forces across India.</p>
