<h2 id="vehere">Vehere</h2>
<p>Vehere is a surveillance technology company founded in 2006. With headquarters in both India and the United States, Vehere provides advanced interception and monitoring services designed to assist telecom companies in intercepting calls and data. </p>
<p>On its official website, Vehere advertises its capability to collect and analyze mass data "from diverse communication network sources, including telephone calls, mobile data, and Internet-based services such as email, voiceover-IP, instant messaging, and others."</p>
