<h2 id="videotec">Videotec</h2>
<p>Videotec was an Italian company that specializes in the design and manufacture of professional video surveillance equipment. During a June 2018 Who Profits field tour in the old city of Jerusalem, Videotec cameras were documented as part of the surveillance system in the occupied area. The company’s official distributer in Israel is Mal-Tech Technological Solutions, a private Israeli company owned by Moshe Amzel. Mal-Tech provides solutions to the Israeli government such as cameras and network devices. It provides equipment to security bodies such as the Israeli army, the Israeli Police and the Israeli Ministry of Defense. In 2022, it was acquired by Motorola Solutions.</p>
