<h2 id="visionlabs">VisionLabs</h2>
<p>VisionLabs is a Russian-founded computer vision developer headquartered in Amsterdam, Netherlands. The company is best known for its facial recognition technology, which is used in over 60 countries for digital identity purposes. In 2021, it was acquired by MTS, Russia’s largest telecoms operator.</p>
