<h2 id="xtend">Xtend</h2>
<p>Xtend is an Israeli drone manufacturer. Their Xtender is a miniature indoor drone controlled via virtual reality goggles, allowing operators to conduct intrusive surveillance missions. Their Scorpio drone is also designed for surveillance and combat. Equipped with cameras, sensors, and even lethal payloads, these drones use Xtend’s OSX operating system for human-assisted autonomy, enabling automated navigation and multi-drone coordination. The company works closely with the U.S Department of Defense as well as the Israeli military.</p>
