<h2 id="zero-security">Zero Security</h2>
<p>Zero Security Research Labs is a zero-day vulnerability reseller that also offers intelligence-gathering systems, including IMSI-catchers and Wi-Fi interception tools. One of their primary products, Xperia-Active, enables the capture of IMSI, IMEI, and TMSI data, as well as real-time communication interception. The company is founded by Andres Acosta, Azizjon Mamashoev, and James Grandoff, and is headquartered in Florida, USA.</p>
